{"tid":679173,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲人寧願訓天橋底 食二手飯都唔去搏坐監?","createTime":"2018-05-26T15:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T01:25:02.000Z","uid":68728,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a29466d1cabed6d5d51db4638dd7064f4419297c","tid":679173,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T15:52:34.000Z","msg":"點解啲人寧願訓天橋底 食二手飯都唔去搏坐監? <br />\n<br />\n係監入面點都好過要訓街啦 包食包住<br />\n入面啲人知你搏坐監又係老野 都應該唔會搞你 <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打 特別係坐過監既解釋下? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(本人絕不鼓勵犯法行為)"},{"pid":"c03c5f7773dc2d3157af31e42591ab1fd586e09e","tid":679173,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T15:55:25.000Z","msg":"唔想臨死都係監躉囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72abe43430e65649d7162a8fc9e3bbd2ad16112","tid":679173,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T15:55:33.000Z","msg":"入面啲江湖人士 知道一個人訓街 冇野食先淪落到去搏坐監都應該唔會搞佢啦?"},{"pid":"0e4d19c57d6bcb37194df15392e6104a99269212","tid":679173,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c03c5f7773dc2d3157af31e42591ab1fd586e09e","tid":679173,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T15:55:25.000Z","msg":"唔想臨死都係監躉囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T15:56:35.000Z","msg":"坐監有病都有得睇 身後事都有人幫手搞埋 <br />\n<br />\n係出面訓街真係死左都冇人理"},{"pid":"02faa58f90101a1fedc4c69ab79e914162289bf0","tid":679173,"uid":186208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"冇自由"},{"pid":"530b30001b8f60ad642968db398e2de715e4de89","tid":679173,"uid":4618,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0e4d19c57d6bcb37194df15392e6104a99269212","tid":679173,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c03c5f7773dc2d3157af31e42591ab1fd586e09e","tid":679173,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"